Get GlotPress POMOs
===================

Downloads .mo and .pot files from completed translations of a specific project on translate.wordpress.org.

Usage
-----

get-translate-pomos.rb PROJECT VERSION
* PROJECT: URL slug for a project listed at http://translate.wordpress.org/projects/. e.g. buddypress
* VERSION: A sub-project, or version, of the PROJECT. e.g. 1.6.x

